<cell alignment="left" valignment="top" topline="true" usebox="none">
\begin_inset Text

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Posem que volem expressar aquesta longitud en forma de fracció irreductible
 
\begin_inset Formula $\nicefrac{a}{b}$
\end_inset

.
 Per tant, volem dos enters 
\begin_inset Formula $a$
\end_inset

 i 
\begin_inset Formula $b$
\end_inset

 tals que 
\begin_inset Formula $(\nicefrac{a}{b})^{2}=2$
\end_inset

.
 O sigui 
\begin_inset Formula $a^{2}=2·b^{2}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\end_inset
</cell>
</row>
<row>
<cell alignment="center" valignment="top" topline="true" usebox="none">
