<cell alignment="left" valignment="top" topline="true" usebox="none">
\begin_inset Text

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Imaginem un conjunt 
\begin_inset Formula $A=\left\{ a_{0},a_{1},a_{2},a_{3},\ldots\right\} $
\end_inset

 (no necessàriament finit) de punts sobre la recta que estigui 
