<cell alignment="left" valignment="top" topline="true" usebox="none">
\begin_inset Text

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Per altra banda, aquest axioma el necessitem per demostrar coses tant aparentmen
t òbvies com que si tenim dos conjunts qualssevol 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

